        "category": "class",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> A rope is within your reach, or you have a rope or grappling weapon in your hand.</p><hr /><p>You've learned to fight confidently while swinging from a line. You take hold of a nearby rope, throw a rope from your hand, or fire a grappling weapon at a solid surface, and then swing up to twice your Speed. You can make a Strike using a one-handed weapon or unarmed attack at any point during this movement. If you critically fail on this Strike, your movement ends at the point you attempted the Strike.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Pirate Dedication] and you boarded or disembarked from a boat or similar vehicle during this movement, the Strike deals one additional weapon damage die.</p>"
        },
